
"""
Stock Inventory Dashboard & Alert System
========================================

A friendly Streamlit app for tracking stock, usage and restocking, with
low-stock alerts. One shared SQLite database, four sections:

  • 📊 Dashboard   — search any item; see every item that has fallen at/below
                     its reorder threshold, with colour-coded bars, suggested
                     reorder amounts, summary metrics and an overview chart.
  • 📦 Stock items — add / edit / delete items; a searchable, detailed table
                     (with in-table bars) and a per-item history drill-down.
  • 🩹 Usage       — record how many units were used on a day; browse the usage
                     history, filtered by date range and product name.
  • 📥 Restocking  — record stock received; browse the restock history, filtered
                     by date range and product name.

Run:
    pip install streamlit pandas plotly
    streamlit run inventoryapp.py
"""

